         <abstract id="aspace_d24a71a3333f72cd9a4743ba2a1dffd9">This collection contains substantial ephemera the Wood family gathered during their years as missionaries in Szechuan Province, from 1920-1937, including textiles and wood. Further materials include a written memoir and digital copies of correspondence and family photographs.</abstract>
